ActCanada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology Act
PrecisAppointment of ERIN M. MAHONEY of Vaughan, Ontario, to be a director of the Canada Foundation for Sustainable Development Technology, to hold office during good behaviour for a term of four years, in the place of Kenneth Ross Creelman, whose term has expired.
